  "title": "BIM Coordinator (M&E)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Develop project models and construction documents using BIM software and ensure accurate updates to Revit models, including coordination drawings.</li>\n  <li>Create 2D and 3D shop drawings, as-built drawings, and ensure timely updates to project documentation.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with the Project Document Controller to facilitate accurate data transfer and ensure consistency in documentation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess BIM certificate.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience as a <strong>BIM Coordinator</strong> in <strong>Large Construction Projects.</strong></li>\n  <li>Proficient in <strong>Revit</strong> and<strong> Navisworks.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
